speaker: Venitra
title: ONNX Runtime speeds up Image Embedding model in Bing Semantic Precise Image Search
description:
Accelerate and optimize machine learning models regardless of training framework using ONNX and ONNX Runtime. This episode introduces both ONNX and ONNX Runtime and provides an example of ONNX Runtime accelerating Bing Semantic Precise Image Search.

Show Summary:
[0:00] – Introduction to ONNX
[3:40] – Getting Started with ONNX
[4:15] – Demo: Convert a CoreML Model to ONNX
[6:25] – Introduction to ONNX Runtime
[8:30] – ONNX Versions and Operator Sets (Opsets)
[10:20] – ONNX Runtime Hardware Acceleration
[11:20] – Case Study: ONNX Runtime + Bing Semantic Precise Image Search
